<!-- ==========================================================
(Search Notes Page)

Description:
Template for displaying the note search interface for users.
Allows filtering, sorting, and pagination of notes.
Supports both guest and authenticated users with localized text.

Responsibilities:
- Provide input for searching notes by title/content.
- Include a filter panel for sorting notes:
  • Newest First / Oldest First
  • Alphabetically A-Z / Z-A
- Display search results in a paginated list.
- Show empty state message when no results are found.
- Handle guest and authenticated note data transparently.

Structure:
1. Search input and title
2. Filter toggle button and hidden filter panel
3. Empty state message placeholder
4. Results container (ul) for notes
5. Pagination container

Client-Side Behavior:
- Input triggers live filtering via search.js
- Filter buttons trigger sorting without page reload
- Pagination buttons dynamically update the displayed notes
- Empty state displayed when the filtered list is empty
- Supports i18n for all text and placeholders

Dependencies:
- search.js (handles search, filters, sorting, pagination)
- auth.js and Firebase Firestore (for authenticated user notes)
- i18n system for multi-language support
- Global bundle.min.js

Accessibility & Usability Notes:
- Filter panel is toggled via button and visually hidden/shown
- Buttons and inputs include clear labels for screen readers
- Pagination ensures users can navigate large note lists efficiently

========================================================== -->

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="search">
    <div class="search__Cont">
        <h2 class="search__titulo" data-i18n="buscarSearch"></h2>

        <input class="search__input" type="text" id="search" placeholder="Search notes..." data-i18n-placeholder="search_placeholder">
    </div>

    <!-- 🟦 FILTER BUTTON -->
    <div class="search__filter">
        <button id="filterToggle" class="search__filter--btn" data-i18n="filters">
            🔽 
        </button>

        <!-- HIDDEN FILTER PANEL -->
        <div id="filterPanel" class="search__filter--panel hidden">
            <h3 data-i18n="order_by"></h3>

            <button class="search__filter--option" data-sort="date-desc" data-i18n="newest_first"></button>
            <button class="search__filter--option" data-sort="date-asc" data-i18n="oldest_first"></button>
            <button class="search__filter--option" data-sort="alpha-asc" data-i18n="a_z"></button>
            <button class="search__filter--option" data-sort="alpha-desc" data-i18n="z_a"></button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- EMPTY STATE MESSAGE -->
    <p id="empty-state" class="no-results" data-i18n="findlist"></p>

    <!-- SEARCH RESULTS -->
    <ul class="search__results" id="results"></ul>

    <!-- PAGINATION -->
    <div class="search__pagination" id="pagination"></div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>